title: Photograph, "Trude and John  for the Project "Faces"", ca. 1974
creditline: Gift of Mr. Eric and Mrs. Sylvia Elsesser, The Trude Guermonprez Archives
description: Black and white photograph of Trude Guermonprez  and  her husband John Elsesser in profile facing left:  Trude in foreground, John behind and a little forward of Trude.
